ere quite involved, we can give\ndirect proofs using graph matrices and our norm bounds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Apr 2016 14:31:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 5 Sep 2016 15:55:45 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 21 Feb 2020 09:10:25 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sat, 10 Oct 2020 02:01:43 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Thu, 29 Apr 2021 16:36:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-30"}
