erties of the NEO populations, as well as simulated cadences and\ntelescope performance estimates provided by LSST. We further show that while\nneither LSST nor a space-based IR platform like NEOCam individually can\ncomplete the survey for 140m diameter NEOs, the combination of these systems\ncan achieve that goal after a decade of observation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Apr 2016 15:33:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-08"}
